reviewText: Camp Nowhere funny and probably the best of the three.  My  Father the Hero with a very young Katherine Heigl and always likeable Gerard Depardieu is enjoyable.  Secret of the Lost Legend is not PG, not suitable for anybody under 14 even these days due to lengthy scenes displaying topless native women of all ages, otherwise it is a strictly B science-fictionay flick.  The 4 stars are for the other two movies.
summary: Nostalgic three, entertaining but not PG
